            <title><![CDATA[Miyamoto Can't Get This Nintendo Movie Idea Out Of His Head]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/miyamoto-cant-get-this-nintendo-movie-idea-out-of-his-head/1100-6531710/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
